content.rendered:
Directed by Pushpdeep Bhardwaj. Lal Mohan

Written by Pushpdeep Bhardwaj. Kausar Munir. Suhrita Sengupta

Cast Rhea Chakraborty (Miss Aisha Pradhan). Varun Mitra (Dev Mathur). Digangana Suryavanshi (Anu D Mathur). Arya Poorti (Renu). Mahesh Thakur (Mr. Pradhan -Aisha’s Father) . Farida Dadi (Old couple on train). Pravina Bhagwat Deshpande (Dev’s Mother (as Praveena Deshpande)). Aanya Dureja (Self). Sanchay Goswami (Arjun’s Friend). Yusuf Hussain (Old couple on train). Arjun Kanungo (Arjun). Mohammad Salman Khan (Salman). Abhishek Khanna (JP Mishra, Coach Attendant). Jashan Singh Kohli (Sunny Singh). Vikash Rajput (Vikash Rajput). VJimmy Sharma (Rocky (as Jimmy Sharma)). Sonali Sudan (Mrs. Simran Sunny Singh). Chayan Trivedi (T.T.E.). Rajsi Verma

Language Hindi

Producers Mahesh Bhatt. Mukesh Bhatt. Sakshi Bhatt. Sumit Sabharwal. Kumkum Saigal

Production Vishesh Film
